data.title: FALLEN ANGELS by Niven, Pournelle, & Flynn (1991) PB ~Earth's New Ice Age~
data.meta_description: Jerry Pournelle. Larry Niven. FALLEN ANGELS. ABOUT THIS BOOK: 2073. Earth falls victim to a new ice age and paradoxically, the Green politicians have rejected the technology that could save the planet.
